The paper deals with the performance analysis of a detection algorithm in large MIMO systems, which is a topic that falls under the information theory (cs.IT) and networking and internet architecture (cs.NI) sub-categories. The use of V-BLAST and 4-QAM suggests that the paper may also be relevant to the signal processing (cs.SI) and computer engineering (cs.CE) sub-categories. Finally, the mention of Rayleigh fading and the use of multiple antennas suggests that the paper may also be relevant to the multimedia (cs.MM) sub-category.
